OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FRather cold with a mix of sunny
OL,6,Fspells and frequent blustery showers,
OL,7,Fwhich will be heavy at times with a
OL,8,Frisk of hail and thunder. Breezy near
OL,9,Fthe coast with occasionally strong
OL,10,Fnorthwesterly winds.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FSome late sunny spells, then
OL,13,Fclear spells overnight, with showers,
OL,14,Fthe showers becoming less frequent and
OL,15,Flighter. Touch of frost possible in
OL,16,Fsheltered spots, but breezy near
OL,17,Fcoasts.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
