OL,3,GStrathclyde
OL,4,
OL,5,CThursday:FAnother rather cold day with
OL,6,Fa mix of sunny spells and occasionally
OL,7,Fheavy showers, the showers tending to
OL,8,Fbecome less heavy through the
OL,9,Fafternoon and evening. Remaining
OL,10,Fbreezy near coasts.
OL,11,
OL,12,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers
OL,13,Fand winds ease from west Friday.
OL,14,FBright start Saturday cloud and rain
OL,15,Fedging east in afternoon. Morning rain
OL,16,FSunday then sunny spells and a few
OL,17,Fshowers in the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
